        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURES 35–39. Megarthrus heise sp. nov. with anal pedicels of deutonymphs of Uropodina mites: head and anterior part of pronotum of the same specimen in dorsal (35) and oblique (36) views with pedicel on left eye; elytra and abdomen in dorsal view of specimen with pedicels on elytra and abdomen (37); pronotum in dorsal view of specimen with pedicel on pronotum (38); elytra in latetal view of specimen with pedicel on elytra (39). Scale bar = 0.2 mm; up = 35–36, 38–39; down = 37." ;
